{"tid":1974592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳法院判警方查記者手令無效","createTime":"2020-04-16T03:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T05:52:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e55359051a6f1643d8cb83eb3747975f1af8731","tid":1974592,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200416/KE7VVLS7M2NZXVJ5ECP5DL56SI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200416%2FKE7VVLS7M2NZXVJ5ECP5DL56SI%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=2b6111df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200416%2FKE7VVLS7M2NZXVJ5ECP5DL56SI%2F&h=e5ffd5b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200416/KE7VVLS7M2NZXVJ5ECP5DL56SI/</a><br />\n<br />\n澳法院判警方查記者手令無效<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200416/large/1586968222_5134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200416%2Flarge%2F1586968222_5134.jpg&h=e5444463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斯梅瑟斯特曾披露政府監控國民計劃。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲聯邦警察去年搜查披露政府監控國民計劃的記者寓所，引發公眾對新聞自由受打壓之慮，最高法院昨日裁定有關搜查令無效，卻未要求警方銷毀從該次搜查獲得的證據。<br />\n<br />\n警可起訴涉事記者<br />\n<br />\n高等法院七名法官一致認為搜查令無效，警方搜查行動及從涉案新聞集團（News Corp）記者斯梅瑟斯特（Annika Smethurst）電話及電腦取得資料違法，因該令狀未能準確陳述斯梅瑟斯特所涉罪行。然而，高院法官因意見分歧，駁回斯梅瑟斯特要求銷毀有關證物的申請，亦無裁定搜查行動侵犯她的「政治傳播自由」，意味着警方仍可起訴她，並將有關證物呈堂。警方稱證物目前被「隔離」，探員從未翻閱。<br />\n<br />\n斯梅瑟斯特引用政府機密文件、指內政部及國防部提出賦予情報機構國防信號局（ASD）權力，秘密獲取澳洲公民電郵、銀行戶口及短訊資料的報道前年4月面世，內政部長登頓其後證實有此計劃。然而，警方去年6月接連搜查斯梅瑟斯特寓所及國營澳洲廣播公司（ABC）總部，後者2017年揭發澳洲特種部隊涉於阿富汗殺害無辜男性和兒童時，亦引援了政府機密文件。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"c15a521c4dfc07c824500aa77ec1caa5ed454382","tid":1974592,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"香港都係?"},{"pid":"1bf2938054e5afa23b6cf4e19b70f501df82bd10","tid":1974592,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"澳洲案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b074d6bab9187d2b431b96e9dee2f398fdf5235b","tid":1974592,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15a521c4dfc07c824500aa77ec1caa5ed454382","tid":1974592,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"香港都係?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"香港要你跪"}]}